snippet.title: SPY x FAMILY OP: Mixed Nuts [ Lofi Remix ]
snippet.description:
Original Song from the Opening Theme to TV Anime "SPY x FAMILY" Titled "Mixed Nuts" ("ミックスナッツ") Originally by Official Hige Dism ("Official髭男dism")

Art by Sonia: https://instagram.com/soniaaart_

Now out on Spotify, Apple Music, and more!
https://dj-jo.com/MixedNutsLofi

BPM: 111
Genres: Lofi / Chill Hop

---
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/djjomusic
Support my Patreon for high quality mp3 downloads and uncompressed instrumentals!
---

I am LOVING this show so far! Good vibes all around! I'm excited to see how the show progresses this season!! Such a cute series!

I really gotta listen to Official髭男dism more often too! I already know about their song cry baby but I haven't started the anime it's from. Lots on my watch list hahaha

I hope everyone enjoys this arrangement and the new episode today!

Until next time!

#spyxfamily #spyxfamilyanime
